As Kirk, McCoy, Sulu and geologist D'Amato beam over to a geologically unique

flung nearly a thousand light years across the galaxy. The woman soon re-appears,
both on the Enterprise and on the planet, killing D'Amato and Engineer Watson.

while the Enterprise, endeavoring to return, faces possible destruction from
sabotage of their warp engines.
